I was more worried it was a request for something like a circuit diagram for Rug Rage or Maize Craze. Hint there probably isn’t a true one, the best I could ever find was this sketch in the game manual for 1993. There are pinouts for the standard kit hardware after.

Edit: If 2014 is ancient I’m Ancient -2. Still feels old. I joined FRC at the tail end 2012 season just in time to graduate after 2013, become a mentor and then have them system all change over to the RoboRio, PDP, VRM as soon as I got the hang of the CRIO system top to bottom.
